@startuml 12-complete-microservice-architecture
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam wrapWidth 200
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 15
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center

title Healthcare Insurance PA Platform - Complete Microservice Architecture\nEnd-to-End Flow with All Components (55+ Services, 6 Databases, 11 AI Agents)

actor "Provider\nOffice Staff" as Provider
participant "Web Portal\n(React)" as Portal #LightBlue
box "API Gateway Layer (Kong Enterprise)" #LightGray
    participant "Auth\nGateway" as AuthGW
    participant "Rate Limit\nGateway" as RateLimitGW
    participant "LLM\nGateway" as LLMGW
end box

box "Orchestration Layer" #LightGreen
    participant "Workflow\nEngine\n(LangGraph)" as Workflow
    participant "Temporal\nServer" as Temporal
end box

box "AI Agent Layer (11 Agents)" #LightYellow
    participant "Intake\nAgent\n(GPT-4o Vision)" as IntakeAgent
    participant "Eligibility\nAgent\n(GPT-3.5)" as EligAgent
    participant "Benefits\nAgent\n(GPT-4o)" as BenefitsAgent
    participant "Clinical\nAgent\n(GPT-4o + RAG)" as ClinicalAgent
    participant "Policy\nAgent\n(Claude 3.5)" as PolicyAgent
    participant "Fraud\nAgent\n(Neo4j + ML)" as FraudAgent
    participant "Decision\nAgent\n(GPT-4o)" as DecisionAgent
    participant "Notification\nAgent" as NotifyAgent
end box

box "Data Services Layer (8 Services)" #LightCyan
    participant "Member\nService" as MemberSvc
    participant "Provider\nService" as ProviderSvc
    participant "Policy\nService" as PolicySvc
    participant "Benefits\nConfig\nService" as BenefitsSvc
    participant "Clinical\nContent\nService" as ClinicalSvc
end box

box "RAG Services Layer" #Wheat
    participant "Vector\nSearch\n(Milvus)" as VectorSearch
    participant "Hybrid\nSearch\n(Elasticsearch)" as HybridSearch
    participant "Graph\nRAG\n(Neo4j)" as GraphRAG
end box

box "Database Layer (6 Systems)" #MistyRose
    database "PostgreSQL\n(6 TB)\n6 databases\n30+ tables" as PostgreSQL
    database "Redis\n(26 GB)\nCache + State" as Redis
    database "Milvus\n(1.2 TB)\n10M vectors" as Milvus
    database "Neo4j\n(200 GB)\nKnowledge Graph" as Neo4j
    database "Elasticsearch\n(400 GB)\nFull-text Search" as Elasticsearch
    database "Azure Blob\n(10 TB)\nDocuments" as BlobStorage
end box

database "Kafka\nEvent Bus" as Kafka

== PHASE 1: INTAKE & DOCUMENT PROCESSING (2 minutes) ==

Provider -> Portal: 1. Submit PA Request\n(Upload PDF, clinical notes)\nHTTPS POST /api/v1/pa/submit
activate Portal

Portal -> AuthGW: 2. Authenticate\nOAuth2 JWT token
activate AuthGW
AuthGW -> Redis: Validate session\nGET session:{token}
AuthGW --> Portal: Authenticated ✓
deactivate AuthGW

Portal -> RateLimitGW: 3. Check rate limit
activate RateLimitGW
RateLimitGW -> Redis: INCR ratelimit:{client_id}
RateLimitGW --> Portal: Allowed (23/100)
deactivate RateLimitGW

Portal -> BlobStorage: 4. Upload documents\nPUT physician_order.pdf\n(2.5 MB)
activate BlobStorage
BlobStorage --> Portal: Blob URL
deactivate BlobStorage

Portal -> PostgreSQL: 5. Create PA case\nINSERT INTO pa_cases\ncase_id='PA-2026-123456'
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> Portal: Case created ✓
deactivate PostgreSQL

Portal -> Kafka: 6. Publish event\nTopic: pa.case.created
activate Kafka
Kafka --> Portal: Event queued
deactivate Kafka

Portal --> Provider: PA Request Submitted\nCase ID: PA-2026-123456\n(T+170ms)
deactivate Portal

Kafka -> Workflow: 7. Consume event\npa.case.created
activate Workflow

Workflow -> Redis: 8. Initialize state\nSETEX working_memory:{case_id}
activate Redis
Redis --> Workflow: State stored
deactivate Redis

Workflow -> Temporal: 9. Start workflow\nPAWorkflow\nTimeout: 30 min
activate Temporal
Temporal -> PostgreSQL: Persist workflow state
Temporal --> Workflow: Workflow started
deactivate Temporal

Workflow -> IntakeAgent: 10. Invoke Intake Agent\ngRPC call
activate IntakeAgent

IntakeAgent -> BlobStorage: Fetch document\nphysician_order.pdf
activate BlobStorage
BlobStorage --> IntakeAgent: PDF content (2.5 MB)
deactivate BlobStorage

IntakeAgent -> LLMGW: 11. LLM Call #1:\nDocument Classification\n"Classify this document"
activate LLMGW
LLMGW -> Redis: Check cache\nGET llm_cache:{hash}
LLMGW --> LLMGW: Cache MISS
LLMGW -> LLMGW: Route to GPT-4o Vision
note right: OpenAI API\ngpt-4o-2024-05-13\nTemp: 0.0\nTokens: 500\n2.1s latency
LLMGW --> IntakeAgent: {type: "physician_order",\nconfidence: 0.98}
deactivate LLMGW

IntakeAgent -> IntakeAgent: 12. Azure Form Recognizer\nOCR processing\n3.5s latency
note right: Extract:\n- member_id: M-987654321\n- provider_npi: 1234567890\n- diagnosis: M54.5\n- procedure: 72148\n- clinical notes

IntakeAgent -> LLMGW: 13. LLM Call #2:\nEntity Extraction\nStructured output (Pydantic)
activate LLMGW
LLMGW -> LLMGW: GPT-4o\nTemp: 0.1\nTokens: 2000\n1.8s
LLMGW --> IntakeAgent: Extracted entities JSON
deactivate LLMGW

IntakeAgent -> PostgreSQL: 14. Store extracted data\nUPDATE pa_cases\nSET extracted_data=...
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> IntakeAgent: Updated ✓
deactivate PostgreSQL

IntakeAgent -> Redis: 15. Update working memory\nHSET agents:intake_agent
activate Redis
Redis --> IntakeAgent: Stored
deactivate Redis

IntakeAgent --> Workflow: Intake complete ✓\n(T+7.6s)
deactivate IntakeAgent

== PHASE 2: ELIGIBILITY VERIFICATION (15 seconds) ==

Workflow -> EligAgent: 16. Invoke Eligibility Agent
activate EligAgent

EligAgent -> MemberSvc: 17. Get member data\ngRPC MemberService/GetMember\nmember_id='M-987654321'
activate MemberSvc

MemberSvc -> Redis: 18. Cache check\nGET cache:member:{id}
activate Redis
Redis --> MemberSvc: Cache HIT ✓\n(2ms, TTL: 2400s)
deactivate Redis

MemberSvc --> EligAgent: Member data:\n{name, dob, plan_id,\nenrollment_status: "Active"}
deactivate MemberSvc

EligAgent -> PostgreSQL: 19. COB check\nSELECT * FROM\ncoordination_of_benefits
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> EligAgent: No secondary insurance
deactivate PostgreSQL

EligAgent -> LLMGW: 20. LLM Call #3:\nEligibility Decision\nGPT-3.5 Turbo (0.8s)
activate LLMGW
LLMGW --> EligAgent: {eligible: true,\nreason: "Active enrollment"}
deactivate LLMGW

EligAgent -> Redis: 21. Store result
activate Redis
Redis --> EligAgent: Stored
deactivate Redis

EligAgent --> Workflow: Eligible ✓ (T+8.4s)
deactivate EligAgent

== PHASE 3: BENEFITS DETERMINATION (20 seconds) ==

Workflow -> BenefitsAgent: 22. Invoke Benefits Agent
activate BenefitsAgent

BenefitsAgent -> PolicySvc: 23. Get policy\nGET /policies/PLAN-2024-GOLD
activate PolicySvc
PolicySvc -> PostgreSQL: SELECT * FROM plan_policies
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> PolicySvc: Policy rules (15 KB JSON)
deactivate PostgreSQL
PolicySvc --> BenefitsAgent: Policy data
deactivate PolicySvc

BenefitsAgent -> BenefitsSvc: 24. Get benefits config\nGET /benefits/{plan}/MRI
activate BenefitsSvc
BenefitsSvc -> PostgreSQL: SELECT copay, coinsurance,\ndeductible, oop_max
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> BenefitsSvc: {copay: 0, coinsurance: 0.20,\ndeductible: 2000, oop_max: 8000}
deactivate PostgreSQL
BenefitsSvc --> BenefitsAgent: Benefits config
deactivate BenefitsSvc

BenefitsAgent -> LLMGW: 25. LLM Call #4:\nCost Calculation\nGPT-4o with code interpreter
activate LLMGW
LLMGW --> BenefitsAgent: {estimated_charge: 1500,\nmember_responsibility: 940,\nplan_pays: 560}
deactivate LLMGW

BenefitsAgent -> ProviderSvc: 26. Network tier check\nGET /network/check?npi=...
activate ProviderSvc
ProviderSvc -> PostgreSQL: SELECT tier FROM\nnetwork_contracts
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> ProviderSvc: {tier: "In-Network Tier 1"}
deactivate PostgreSQL
ProviderSvc --> BenefitsAgent: Network tier
deactivate ProviderSvc

BenefitsAgent -> Redis: 27. Store decision
BenefitsAgent --> Workflow: Benefits approved ✓\n(T+10.7s)
deactivate BenefitsAgent

== PHASE 4: CLINICAL REVIEW WITH RAG (8 minutes - BOTTLENECK) ==

Workflow -> ClinicalAgent: 28. Invoke Clinical Agent
activate ClinicalAgent

ClinicalAgent -> LLMGW: 29. LLM Call #5:\nGenerate search query\n"MRI lumbar spine medical necessity..."
activate LLMGW
LLMGW --> ClinicalAgent: Search query string (1.2s)
deactivate LLMGW

ClinicalAgent -> LLMGW: 30. Generate embedding\ntext-embedding-ada-002
activate LLMGW
LLMGW --> ClinicalAgent: 1536-dim vector (0.3s)
deactivate LLMGW

par Parallel RAG Retrieval
    ClinicalAgent -> VectorSearch: 31a. Vector search\nsearch(query_embedding,\nlimit=20)
    activate VectorSearch
    VectorSearch -> Milvus: HNSW search\nCOSINE similarity
    activate Milvus
    Milvus --> VectorSearch: Top 20 guidelines\n(45ms, scores: 0.92, 0.89...)
    deactivate Milvus
    VectorSearch --> ClinicalAgent: Vector results
    deactivate VectorSearch
else
    ClinicalAgent -> HybridSearch: 31b. BM25 search\nmulti_match query
    activate HybridSearch
    HybridSearch -> Elasticsearch: Full-text search\nfields: [guideline_text^2,\nspecialty]
    activate Elasticsearch
    Elasticsearch --> HybridSearch: Top 20 guidelines\n(85ms, BM25 scores)
    deactivate Elasticsearch
    HybridSearch --> ClinicalAgent: BM25 results
    deactivate HybridSearch
else
    ClinicalAgent -> GraphRAG: 31c. Graph traversal\nCypher query
    activate GraphRAG
    GraphRAG -> Neo4j: MATCH (Diagnosis)\n-[:REQUIRES]->\n(Procedure)\n-[:HAS_CRITERIA]->\n(Guideline)
    activate Neo4j
    Neo4j --> GraphRAG: 5 guidelines\n(120ms)
    deactivate Neo4j
    GraphRAG --> ClinicalAgent: Graph results
    deactivate GraphRAG
end

ClinicalAgent -> ClinicalAgent: 32. Reciprocal Rank Fusion\nMerge 45 results → Top 10\nRRF score = Σ(1/(k+rank))\nk=60, 15ms
note right: Top 10 reranked:\n- MCG-A-0582 (0.035)\n- IQ-OP-123 (0.031)\n- ...

ClinicalAgent -> ClinicalSvc: 33. Retrieve full text\nGET /guidelines?ids=[...]
activate ClinicalSvc
ClinicalSvc -> PostgreSQL: SELECT guideline_text\nFROM clinical_guidelines\nWHERE id IN (...)
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> ClinicalSvc: 10 guidelines\n(~15,000 tokens, 45ms)
deactivate PostgreSQL
ClinicalSvc --> ClinicalAgent: Full guideline texts
deactivate ClinicalSvc

ClinicalAgent -> LLMGW: 34. LLM Call #6:\nMedical Necessity Review\nGPT-4o 128k context\nPrompt: "Based on these\nguidelines, determine if\nMRI is medically necessary..."
activate LLMGW
note right: Input:\n- 15,000 tokens (guidelines)\n- Clinical summary\n- Patient demographics\nTemp: 0.2\nMax tokens: 2000\nLatency: 4.5s
LLMGW --> ClinicalAgent: {decision: "Approve",\nrationale: "Patient meets\nMCG A-0582 criteria:\n6+ weeks conservative\ntreatment failure,\nradicular symptoms...",\nguidelines_cited:\n["MCG-A-0582", "IQ-OP-123"],\nconfidence: 0.94}
deactivate LLMGW

ClinicalAgent -> ClinicalAgent: 35. Guardrails AI\nHallucination check\nSemantic similarity\nvs source guidelines\n1.2s
note right: Safety evaluation:\n- No hallucination detected\n- Confidence: 0.96\n- Citations verified ✓

ClinicalAgent -> PostgreSQL: 36. Store decision
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> ClinicalAgent: Stored
deactivate PostgreSQL

ClinicalAgent -> Redis: 37. Update state
ClinicalAgent --> Workflow: Medical necessity\napproved ✓ (T+18.1s)
deactivate ClinicalAgent

== PHASE 5: POLICY & FRAUD ANALYSIS (Parallel, 3 minutes) ==

par Policy & Fraud in Parallel
    Workflow -> PolicyAgent: 38. Invoke Policy Agent
    activate PolicyAgent
    PolicyAgent -> PolicyAgent: Claude 3.5 Sonnet\nPolicy compliance check\nSearch exclusions,\nstep therapy, PA rules\n2.5 minutes
    PolicyAgent --> Workflow: Policy compliant ✓
    deactivate PolicyAgent
else
    Workflow -> FraudAgent: 39. Invoke Fraud Agent
    activate FraudAgent
    FraudAgent -> Neo4j: Cypher query:\nProvider billing patterns\nCompare to peer group
    activate Neo4j
    Neo4j --> FraudAgent: Statistics:\nclaim_count, avg_amount,\npeer comparison (200ms)
    deactivate Neo4j
    FraudAgent -> FraudAgent: Isolation Forest\nAnomaly detection ML\nFeatures: [claim_count,\navg_amount, stddev]\n10ms
    FraudAgent --> Workflow: {fraud_risk: "Low",\nscore: 0.12}
    deactivate FraudAgent
end

== PHASE 6: FINAL DECISION (1 minute) ==

Workflow -> DecisionAgent: 40. Invoke Decision Agent
activate DecisionAgent

DecisionAgent -> Redis: 41. Retrieve all agent results\nHGETALL agents
activate Redis
Redis --> DecisionAgent: 7 agent outputs:\n- Intake ✓\n- Eligibility ✓\n- Benefits ✓\n- Clinical ✓\n- Policy ✓\n- Fraud ✓\n- COM ✓
deactivate Redis

DecisionAgent -> LLMGW: 42. LLM Call #12:\nAggregate decision\nGPT-4o synthesis
activate LLMGW
note right: Prompt:\n"Synthesize final PA decision\nfrom 7 agent outputs..."\nAll checks passed ✓
LLMGW --> DecisionAgent: {decision: "APPROVED",\nconfidence: 0.94,\nauth_number:\n"AUTH-2026-123456",\nvalid_through:\n"2026-09-01",\nrequires_human_review:\nfalse}
deactivate LLMGW

DecisionAgent -> DecisionAgent: 43. HITL Routing\nDrools rules engine:\n- confidence < 0.85?\n  → NO (0.94)\n- fraud_risk > 0.30?\n  → NO (0.12)\n- decision = DENIED?\n  → NO (APPROVED)\nResult: Skip human review
note right: Risk-based routing:\n✓ High confidence\n✓ Low fraud risk\n✓ Approved decision\n→ No human review needed

DecisionAgent -> PostgreSQL: 44. Update case\nUPDATE pa_cases\nSET decision='APPROVED',\nauth_number='AUTH-2026-123456',\nstatus='completed'
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> DecisionAgent: Updated ✓
deactivate PostgreSQL

DecisionAgent --> Workflow: Final decision: APPROVED ✓\n(T+14m 30s)
deactivate DecisionAgent

== PHASE 7: NOTIFICATION & AUDIT (1 minute) ==

Workflow -> NotifyAgent: 45. Invoke Notification Agent
activate NotifyAgent

NotifyAgent -> NotifyAgent: 46. Generate PDF\nJinja2 template +\nWeasyPrint\nDecision letter (125 KB)\n1.2s

NotifyAgent -> BlobStorage: 47. Store PDF\nPUT decision letter\n/decisions/2026/06/\nPA-2026-123456-decision.pdf
activate BlobStorage
BlobStorage --> NotifyAgent: PDF URL
deactivate BlobStorage

NotifyAgent -> NotifyAgent: 48. Send email\nSendGrid API\nTo: provider, member\nAttach: decision.pdf\n350ms

NotifyAgent -> Portal: 49. WebSocket push\nReal-time notification\n"Your PA was approved"\n50ms

NotifyAgent -> Kafka: 50. Publish event\npa.case.completed
activate Kafka
Kafka --> NotifyAgent: Published
deactivate Kafka

NotifyAgent --> Workflow: Notifications sent ✓
deactivate NotifyAgent

Workflow -> PostgreSQL: 51. Audit trail\nINSERT INTO case_events\n+ Blockchain (Hyperledger)
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> Workflow: Logged ✓
deactivate PostgreSQL

Workflow -> Temporal: 52. Complete workflow\nStatus: COMPLETED\nDuration: 14m 32s
activate Temporal
Temporal --> Workflow: Finalized
deactivate Temporal

Workflow --> Provider: 53. PA APPROVED ✓\nAuth#: AUTH-2026-123456\nValid through: 2026-09-01\n(via email + portal)
deactivate Workflow

note over Provider, BlobStorage
**WORKFLOW COMPLETE**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
**Business Outcome**: PA Request Approved
**Technical Metrics**:
- Total duration: 14 minutes 32 seconds (under 30-min SLA)
- Microservices invoked: 27+ services
- AI agents executed: 7 agents
- LLM calls: 12 (5 GPT-4o, 6 GPT-3.5, 1 Claude)
- Total tokens: 47,523 tokens
- LLM cost: $0.95
- Database queries: 38 queries
- Cache hits: 12 (75% hit rate)
- Databases accessed: All 6 systems
- Automation: 100% (no human review needed)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
end note

legend right
|= Component |= Technology |= Purpose |
| **Presentation** | React, Node.js | Web UI, Mobile API |
